Class SaveLoco

java.lang.Object
com.github.freddyyj.randomtrainsimworld2.config.SaveLoco
public class SaveLoco
extends Object
Class for managing savefile. Don't create this object. Use Main.setSaveFilePath(String) or Main.saveAs(String) instead.
